## Compile on Windows, MacOS, Linux (with X11)

```bash
mkdir build
cd build
cmake ..
make
```

## Compile for Linux with no X11 (console only)

```bash
mkdir build
cd build
cmake -DNO_X11 ..
make
```

## Compile as WASM

```bash
mkdir build
cd build
cmake .. -DCMAKE_TOOLCHAIN_FILE=$EMSDK/upstream/emscripten/cmake/Modules/Platform/Emscripten.cmake
make
```